{
  "texts": [
    "Without the capacity to draw connections between different pieces of information, GenAI's utility in fostering a deeper understanding of subjects among students is questionable.Addressing these challenges requires innovative approaches to training and implementing GenAI in educational contexts.",
    "Our future research aims to explore the training of GenAI using fine-tuning methods, where seminal articles related to specific subjects are presented.",
    "By integrating such foundational texts into GenAI's knowledge base, we aim to enhance its reasoning capabilities and its ability to generate content that is not only relevant but also rich in insights.",
    "Employing a Socratic method, where students engage with GenAI through questioning, could further this goal.",
    "This approach encourages critical thinking and allows students to explore topics in-depth, facilitating a more meaningful learning experience.Integrating GenAI into the classroom presents a unique opportunity for educators to enhance learning experiences, particularly in complex and interdisciplinary fields such as environmental science."
  ]
}